{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration.getPropertyPriority()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/getPropertyPriority","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model\">CSS Object Model</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/length\"><code>length</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/parentRule\"><code>parentRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/getPropertyCSSValue\"><code>getPropertyCSSValue()</code></a></li><li><em><code>getPropertyPriority()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/getPropertyValue\"><code>getPropertyValue()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/item\"><code>item()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/msGetPropertyEnabled\"><code>msGetPropertyEnabled()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/msPutPropertyEnabled\"><code>msPutPropertyEnabled()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/removeProperty\"><code>removeProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/setProperty\"><code>setProperty()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for CSSOM</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS\"><code>CSS</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframeRule\"><code>CSSKeyframeRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule\"><code>CSSStyleRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><strong>CSSStyleDeclaration.getPropertyPriority() </strong>方法会根据传入的 CSS 属性，返回一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> 来表示该属性的优先级。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>priority</em> = <em>style</em>.getPropertyPriority(<em>property</em>);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><em><code>property</code></em> 是一个<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a>，表示要检查的属性名。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><em>priority</em></code> 是一个<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a>，用以表示属性优先级。存在，就返回（例如：<code>\"important\"</code>）；不存在，则返回空字符串。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下面的代码检查了<code>margin</code>，在 CSS 规则中是否被设置为 important 优先级。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> declaration <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>styleSheets<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>cssRules<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> isImportant <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> declaration<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getPropertyPriority</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'margin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">'important'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"标准","title":"标准","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom/#dom-cssstyledeclaration-getpropertypriority\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">CSSStyleDeclaration.getPropertyPriority()</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Style/css.html#CSS-CSSStyleDeclaration\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Style Specification<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">CSSStyleDeclaration</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsolete</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.CSSStyleDeclaration.getPropertyPriority","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/getPropertyPriority/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"},{"text":"标准","id":"标准"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"CSSStyleDeclaration.getPropertyPriority() 方法会根据传入的 CSS 属性，返回一个 DOMString 来表示该属性的优先级。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration.getPropertyPriority()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSSStyleDeclaration.getPropertyPriority()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/cssstyledeclaration/getpropertypriority","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/cssstyledeclaration/getpropertypriority/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration","title":"CSSStyleDeclaration"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration/getPropertyPriority","title":"CSSStyleDeclaration.getPropertyPriority()"}],"pageTitle":"CSSStyleDeclaration.getPropertyPriority() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}